import React from 'react';
import { Box, Text, Button } from '@chakra-ui/react';

const ColorOverview = ({ themeColors }) => {
  const {
    black,
    body,
    global,
    hoverBorder,
    lightColor,
    ltColorBackgroundDark,
    ltColorBackgroundDefault,
    ltColorBackgroundLight,
    ltColorBlack,
    ltColorBorderDark,
    ltColorBorderDefault,
    ltColorBorderLight,
    ltColorGray100,
    ltColorGray200,
    ltColorGray300,
    ltColorGray400,
    ltColorGray500,
    ltColorGray600,
    ltColorGray700,
    ltColorGray800,
    ltColorGray900,
    ltColorOverlayDark,
    ltColorOverlayDefault,
    ltColorOverlayTransparent,
    ltColorTextDark,
    ltColorTextDefault,
    ltColorTextLight,
    ltColorTextVeryLight,
    ltColorTransparent,
    ltColorWhite,
    ltShadowWebsiteOverlay,
    ltShadowActive,
    ltShadowDefault,
    outlineColor,
    talkTagColor,
    whiteColor,
  } = themeColors;

  // Function to copy color code to clipboard
  const copyToClipboard = (text) => {
    navigator.clipboard.writeText(text);
  };

  return (
    <Box>
      <Box mb={4}>
        <Text fontSize="lg" fontWeight="bold" mb={2} color="brand.800">
          Additional Theme Colors
        </Text>
        <Box>
          <ColorBox colorName="black" colorValue={black} />
          <ColorBox colorName="body" colorValue={body} />
          <ColorBox colorName="global" colorValue={global} />
          <ColorBox colorName="hoverBorder" colorValue={hoverBorder} />
          <ColorBox colorName="lightColor" colorValue={lightColor} />
          <ColorBox colorName="ltColorBackgroundDark" colorValue={ltColorBackgroundDark} />
          <ColorBox colorName="ltColorBackgroundDefault" colorValue={ltColorBackgroundDefault} />
          <ColorBox colorName="ltColorBackgroundLight" colorValue={ltColorBackgroundLight} />
          <ColorBox colorName="ltColorBlack" colorValue={ltColorBlack} />
          <ColorBox colorName="ltColorBorderDark" colorValue={ltColorBorderDark} />
          <ColorBox colorName="ltColorBorderDefault" colorValue={ltColorBorderDefault} />
          <ColorBox colorName="ltColorBorderLight" colorValue={ltColorBorderLight} />
          <ColorBox colorName="ltColorGray100" colorValue={ltColorGray100} />
          <ColorBox colorName="ltColorGray200" colorValue={ltColorGray200} />
          <ColorBox colorName="ltColorGray300" colorValue={ltColorGray300} />
          <ColorBox colorName="ltColorGray400" colorValue={ltColorGray400} />
          <ColorBox colorName="ltColorGray500" colorValue={ltColorGray500} />
          <ColorBox colorName="ltColorGray600" colorValue={ltColorGray600} />
          <ColorBox colorName="ltColorGray700" colorValue={ltColorGray700} />
          <ColorBox colorName="ltColorGray800" colorValue={ltColorGray800} />
          <ColorBox colorName="ltColorGray900" colorValue={ltColorGray900} />
          <ColorBox colorName="ltColorOverlayDark" colorValue={ltColorOverlayDark} />
          <ColorBox colorName="ltColorOverlayDefault" colorValue={ltColorOverlayDefault} />
          <ColorBox colorName="ltColorOverlayTransparent" colorValue={ltColorOverlayTransparent} />
          <ColorBox colorName="ltColorTextDark" colorValue={ltColorTextDark} />
          <ColorBox colorName="ltColorTextDefault" colorValue={ltColorTextDefault} />
          <ColorBox colorName="ltColorTextLight" colorValue={ltColorTextLight} />
          <ColorBox colorName="ltColorTextVeryLight" colorValue={ltColorTextVeryLight} />
          <ColorBox colorName="ltColorTransparent" colorValue={ltColorTransparent} />
          <ColorBox colorName="ltColorWhite" colorValue={ltColorWhite} />
          <ColorBox colorName="ltShadowWebsiteOverlay" colorValue={ltShadowWebsiteOverlay} />
          <ColorBox colorName="ltShadowActive" colorValue={ltShadowActive} />
          <ColorBox colorName="ltShadowDefault" colorValue={ltShadowDefault} />
          <ColorBox colorName="outlineColor" colorValue={outlineColor} />
          <ColorBox colorName="talkTagColor" colorValue={talkTagColor} />
          <ColorBox colorName="whiteColor" colorValue={whiteColor} />
        </Box>
      </Box>
    </Box>
  );
};

const ColorBox = ({ colorName, colorValue }) => (
  <Box display="flex" alignItems="center" mb={2}>
    <Box w="30px" h="30px" mr={2} bg={colorValue} borderRadius="md" border="1px solid #ccc" />
    <Text color="brand.800" mr={2}>{colorName}</Text>
    <Text color="brand.800">{colorValue}</Text>
    <Button ml={2} size="sm" colorScheme="brand" onClick={() => copyToClipboard(colorValue)}>
      Copy
    </Button>
  </Box>
);

export default ColorOverview;
